data.title: Accelerate Insights with real
data.meta_description: Confluent and Qlik have teamed to help modernize data centers. Stream data from > 40 sources to Confluent for real-time data integration and analytics.
data.text: Production databases fuel many of the most compelling and actionable Kafka enabled analytics use cases, ranging from real-time customer predictions and business insights, to supply chain optimization to operational reporting. Qlik® Data Integration for CDC Streaming is a simple, low-impact solution for converting many sources—such as databases and mainframes—to efficiently prepare data streams for Apache Kafka® and Confluent in real-time. Together we modernize data infrastructures to enable streaming analytics that accelerate insights.
